Class SystemManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • vodsystemfx.classes.SystemManager

  • public class SystemManager
extends java.lang.Object

      • removeProduct

        public static void removeProduct(int removeIndex)
        Used when deleting product. Method goes through all Users and deletes product index on their prrivate lists. Note that privateList[0] is not the same as on globalList[0] When deleting f.ex. globalList[4] all next objects's index drops by -1 so I do exacly same on private lists. Same happends to globalIndex field of Stream
        Parameters:
        removeIndex - - index of product to remove from allProducts list
